Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.56,0:00:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.76,0:00:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望快點清醒的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.83,0:00:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我為什麼會知道這是夢呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.10,0:00:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真的是…夢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.20,0:00:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間的黃昏的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.78,0:01:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行著一段永遠的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.22,0:01:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的指尖繼續探索著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碎片發出光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.07,0:01:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊的抱住胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.31,0:01:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找遺失的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.52,0:01:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用雙手的掌心確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.83,0:01:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相遇在新的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.16,0:01:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間開始流動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.62,0:02:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天為了學生會主辦的\N校園舞會的開會事宜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.43,0:02:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下午開始的課程全部停課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.56,0:02:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此外 參加舞會的來賓請注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.57,0:02:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,參加者休息室\N下午兩點開始開放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.20,0:02:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要使用的來賓\N請到休息室來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.27,0:02:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年的舞會也辦的很盛大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.08,0:02:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學生會做事還做的真是徹底啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩個不去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.55,0:02:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北川同學你要去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.79,0:02:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我今年還在考慮\N到底要不要去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.79,0:02:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美阪 我們一起去怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要跟你去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.00,0:02:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.03,0:02:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是下午放假還真是不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.87,0:03:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 待會出去逛逛吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.84,0:03:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.55,0:03:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.92,0:03:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.83,0:03:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燕尾服真的適合我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.46,0:03:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的啦 祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.80,0:03:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.97,0:03:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.63,0:03:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很適合祐一吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.91,0:03:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.87,0:03:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想說什麼就說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.91,0:03:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒穿上去不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.75,0:03:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會讓妳看看帥氣的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.82,0:03:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 期待吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.92,0:03:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我第一次\N當小舞的護花使者呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.79,0:04:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以第一支舞留給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.70,0:04:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要把妳像女孩子的一面\N展現給大家看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.57,0:04:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這個很適合妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.21,0:04:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.51,0:04:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 很適合妳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.36,0:04:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.03,0:04:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.63,0:04:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳老是自己決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.27,0:04:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能什麼都要靠自己一個人解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.84,0:04:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.04,0:04:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有「可是」喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一在等妳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.49,0:05:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「舞會」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.04,0:05:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,憧憬的舞會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.64,0:05:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後祐一就踩青蛙鬧鐘…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.35,0:05:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.63,0:05:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟我跳支舞嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.17,0:05:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像不是我該待的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.47,0:05:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.61,0:05:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？一個人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.11,0:05:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.38,0:05:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是佐祐理？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.82,0:06:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是真不像妳啊 小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論從怎麼看都像個千金小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.72,0:06:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千金小姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.99,0:06:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.59,0:06:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千金小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.83,0:06:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一也很稱頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.43,0:06:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你穿上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.83,0:06:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 佐祐理呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.43,0:06:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去跟認識的人打招呼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.97,0:06:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.41,0:06:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易來到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.41,0:06:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是我\N也去吸引別人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.61,0:06:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.21,0:06:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約定好的 第一支舞要一起跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.05,0:06:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.22,0:06:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 來跳舞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.79,0:06:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 你會跳嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.76,0:06:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.86,0:06:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興最重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然不是很瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.63,0:06:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳為什麼拒絕參加學生會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳能進學生會的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.61,0:07:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是我現在還有更重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.91,0:07:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.92,0:07:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.42,0:07:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真看不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.29,0:07:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有儀態可言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.96,0:07:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儀態什麼的有什麼關係呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.38,0:07:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞要喝些什麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.88,0:07:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.06,0:07:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.26,0:07:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.73,0:07:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要在這種地方拿劍出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.38,0:08:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 為什麼選在這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.65,0:08:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倉田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.65,0:08:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.69,0:08:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.13,0:08:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.27,0:08:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這個很適合小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.51,0:08:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理 佐祐理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.85,0:08:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.25,0:08:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 佐祐理她沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.76,0:08:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.82,0:08:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.73,0:09:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.31,0:09:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.95,0:09:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手 住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.36,0:09:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.82,0:09:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川澄 是妳嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.99,0:09:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.33,0:09:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特地易準備的洋裝也完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.34,0:09:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽妳解釋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.38,0:09:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的事情跟以往不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也在現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.65,0:10:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有人目擊到妳在那裡\N揮舞著像劍一樣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.76,0:10:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也真的有人受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.29,0:10:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我實在是驚訝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.50,0:10:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳把玻璃打破又把舞會搞砸\N到底是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.23,0:10:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 川澄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也說些話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.34,0:10:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣悶不吭聲\N小舞會被停學的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.38,0:10:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.28,0:10:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川澄 聽好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你被退學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.55,0:10:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退學…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.52,0:10:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在那邊是關心她嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.46,0:10:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倉田也在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.86,0:10:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請聽聽我們對於小舞\N在舞會上的行為的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.17,0:10:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對川澄的處分是不會改變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.24,0:10:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連聽我們解釋都不行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.21,0:10:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要聽什麼解釋呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.51,0:10:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她打破窗戶的理由嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.81,0:11:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞砸舞會的理由嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.32,0:11:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久瀨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.68,0:11:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管理由是什麼都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.59,0:11:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是因為她的行動所造成的\N不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.66,0:11:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不瞭解嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.02,0:11:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道你為什麼要保護\N這樣的學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.96,0:11:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫這樣的學生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.83,0:11:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這學生會到底是為誰存在的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.77,0:11:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了品學兼優的學生的學生會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.74,0:11:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞難道不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的惡行惡狀在\N學生會是很有名的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.94,0:11:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是這一次的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.18,0:11:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不考慮\N她到底是有什麼理由啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果為小舞著想就住手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.55,0:11:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打下去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.49,0:11:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的下場就會跟川澄一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.26,0:11:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.00,0:11:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞是我的好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.80,0:11:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 小舞就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.60,0:11:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.31,0:12:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理由是怎樣都無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.87,0:12:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.54,0:12:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為小舞是我最重要的好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.08,0:12:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想為小舞做一些事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道有錯嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.96,0:12:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要走了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.12,0:12:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我已經不是這裡的學生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該還有些時間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一下子的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.00,0:12:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 一開始真的不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.50,0:12:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼佐祐理會跟妳在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.74,0:12:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳既不親切又會頂撞學生會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.18,0:12:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 佐祐理說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.75,0:12:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.48,0:12:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.39,0:12:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？水瀨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.99,0:12:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.06,0:12:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我漸漸的\N能瞭解佐祐理說的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.43,0:13:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不但把便當分給野狗吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,默默的承受莫須有的罪名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.74,0:13:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的是個不錯的人\N不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.81,0:13:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以她想讓大家\N瞭解妳好的一面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.28,0:13:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這對妳造成多餘的困擾嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.41,0:13:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟佐祐理為了妳所做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.38,0:13:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是多餘的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.42,0:13:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們為妳所做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.92,0:13:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳完全裝作不知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.22,0:13:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理剛才說的話\N妳有聽到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.29,0:13:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是她的好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.26,0:13:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說了妳是她最重要的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.23,0:13:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣妳還裝不知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣佐祐理多可憐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.97,0:13:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉把妳攔下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.91,0:13:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 妳可以走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.01,0:13:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.28,0:13:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道該怎麼做才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.58,0:13:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 我該怎麼做才好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.22,0:13:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把妳現在想的說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為…佐祐裡\N是我最重要的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.63,0:14:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好的珍惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.83,0:14:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.06,0:14:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟佐祐理\N跟祐一在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.37,0:14:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的很想\N三個人一直在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我也會做些什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.31,0:14:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對會讓妳\N回到我們的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說想辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又該做什麼 怎麼做才好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.49,0:14:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.16,0:14:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 佐祐理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.73,0:14:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是來買東西的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.16,0:14:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說佐祐理 小舞呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞的話沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.50,0:14:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟久瀨談一下的話\N他就會瞭解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.20,0:14:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 有件事想跟你商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.97,0:14:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,商量？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.08,0:14:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天 是小舞的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.48,0:14:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願意陪我去挑禮物嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.79,0:15:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去年是送小豬的音樂盒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小豬的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.53,0:15:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有很多小豬天使在飛舞的\N可愛音樂盒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.23,0:15:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…可愛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.13,0:15:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞她非常高興喔\N還說謝謝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.11,0:15:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那應該是客套話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是小舞的誠意喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.18,0:15:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全心全意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.08,0:15:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.68,0:15:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們也送我們想送的東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.39,0:15:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這是最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.19,0:15:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就送個像女孩子的禮物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.76,0:15:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.86,0:15:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.87,0:15:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.93,0:15:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 絕對會很高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我來介紹給各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.54,0:15:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.25,0:16:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛加入學生會的新血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.68,0:16:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倉田佐祐理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.68,0:16:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管她即將要畢業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.42,0:16:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依然依照我們的請求\N加入學生會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.72,0:16:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理 為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.72,0:16:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了…小舞嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.40,0:16:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.86,0:16:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理 我有話對妳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.27,0:16:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.67,0:16:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有些話想跟你談談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是關於小舞的禮物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.01,0:16:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了小舞嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.24,0:16:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.21,0:16:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳要\N跟學生會的那些傢伙在一起？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是到畢業前的這段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不在意喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.52,0:16:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.09,0:16:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.69,0:16:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個禮拜日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好的辦一場生日宴會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後在今天把禮物送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.43,0:16:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,配合時間讓小舞好好的嚇一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.54,0:16:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.87,0:16:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想好像有點來不及的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.74,0:17:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我你的電話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.41,0:17:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等一下有會要開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.45,0:17:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼祐一 待會見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.73,0:17:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理是為了小舞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.36,0:17:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後我還是這樣\N什麼都做不到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.47,0:17:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.30,0:17:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.11,0:17:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安 祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.51,0:17:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼「午安」啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.45,0:17:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳又白吃然後落跑了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.92,0:17:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.15,0:17:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我叫你\N你都當作沒聽到一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.42,0:17:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要再撞倒我了好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.16,0:17:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能用別的方法打招呼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.39,0:17:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說了「午安」了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.93,0:17:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那有什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.36,0:18:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為看到你\N才出聲叫你的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.40,0:18:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有事的話就不要叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.34,0:18:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好過份喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.40,0:18:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.87,0:18:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在找東西喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.74,0:18:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有找到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.18,0:18:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.01,0:18:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不去找不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.95,0:18:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道要找的是什麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.72,0:18:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.19,0:18:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我會到祐一說的\N我會去的地方找看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.82,0:18:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話雖這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.53,0:18:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是還是沒找到吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.06,0:18:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我現在只能這麼做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.63,0:18:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.10,0:18:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.00,0:18:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.71,0:18:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會加油的 謝謝你祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.54,0:18:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那再見啦 亞由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在我並不知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.96,0:18:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.99,0:18:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在能做的\N就是照佐祐理說的做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.10,0:19:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有個叫倉田的女孩\N打過電話來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.01,0:19:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒問佐祐理的電話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.08,0:19:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 她說在校門口等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.72,0:19:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學校校門口嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.90,0:19:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.10,0:19:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在教室嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.58,0:19:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.41,0:19:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.65,0:19:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.79,0:20:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.85,0:20:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到…學校來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經可以回來學校了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.96,0:20:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.80,0:20:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 這真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.00,0:20:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.57,0:20:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.47,0:20:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理跟我說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.97,0:20:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一跟佐祐理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.14,0:20:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了我做了很多的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.87,0:20:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦 我並沒有做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.21,0:20:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是佐祐理在努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.48,0:20:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理總是為我做這麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.28,0:20:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始玻璃被打破的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.48,0:20:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也說小舞是好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.25,0:20:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會這麼作一定有理由的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.72,0:20:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理果然是為了小舞的復學才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.89,0:20:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好珍惜哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩人的心意…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.73,0:20:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞的心意\N還有佐祐理的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.47,0:20:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.41,0:20:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是 之前的鬼怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.35,0:21:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪 沒有來這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.15,0:21:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.26,0:21:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼怪到底是什麼東西啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.73,0:21:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.73,0:21:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布偶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.10,0:21:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…會這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.84,0:22:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐…理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.20,0:22:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從隨風飄流的雲朵之間\N窺視到晴空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.14,0:22:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連熟悉的街道也閃閃發光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.45,0:22:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前奔跑的小小的背影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.83,0:22:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時的兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.80,0:23:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用天真來蓋過溢出的疼痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.41,0:23:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間靜悄悄的流動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.15,0:23:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吹拂著溫柔的風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.72,0:23:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為凍僵的思念也會化做笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.07,0:23:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊佐祐理的鬼怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.71,0:23:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不原諒那些傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.31,0:23:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞卻傷害了自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.88,0:23:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanon第8話  少女的牢籠
